===Etymology===
The obsolete sense of “quota”, from {{bor|en|ML.|quotatio}}, from {{der|en|la|quotāre}}, is attested from the 15th century. The sense “fragment of verbal expression”, attested from the 17th century, may come from this source, or else from the verb {{affix|en|quote|-ation}}.<ref>{{R:Etymonline|quotation}}</ref>

