===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# A fragment of a human expression that is repeated by somebody else, for example from [[literature]] or a famous [[speech]].
#: {{syn|en|quote|citation}}
#: {{ux|en|"Where they burn books, they will also burn people" is a famous '''quotation''' from {{w|Heinrich Heine}}.}}
# A price that has been quoted for buying or selling.
#: {{ux|en|Let's get a '''quotation''' for repairing the roof before we decide whether it's worth doing.}}
# The act of setting a [[price]].
# {{lb|en|obsolete}} A [[quota]], a [[share]].<ref>{{R:Webster 1913|Quotation}}</ref>

